78 YOUNG's Works, in 4 Vols. Containing Love of
Fame.—Last Day.—Paraphrase on Job.—Busiris.—Revenge.—Brothers;
and Centaur.

The principal of these works are Bayle's Historical
and Critical Dictionary; the General Dictionary;
the Biographia Britanniaa; the Athenae Oxonienses;
and Mr. Collier's Historical Dictionary.

